                            <comment id="14643918" author="sumit.nigam" created="Tue, 28 Jul 2015 06:20:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;For spark on yarn, would yarn not remove all local directories created by container processes upon their exit even if it were unclean exit? In such a case, even if spark fails to remove them, yarn should be able to clear them. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
